name: Fugly wireframe design system
description:
Fugly is a fully comprehensive wire framing kit built as a design system for creating low fidelity designs.


With over 130 custom icons and a complete system of components built around variants, Fugly has everything you need to create fast and easy design work.


Get in touch with me: https:www.linkedin.com/in/carl-webb-56a74098/ for requests, things not working or just to say hi :)


Enjoy!
